Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.74,0:01:41.28,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,いこうぜ　Go　ありのままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:43.75,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,Break Out 嵐起こせ
